{"tid":172190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有一熱就痕既人","createTime":"2017-03-25T18:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T03:48:00.000Z","uid":9710,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf22721ca26bddad8c97a2a7cf628a5ecd3039b","tid":172190,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:14:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人年年二月到五月<br />\n十月到十二月左右<br />\n一熱(例如行得急,做運動,沖涼)就會成身痕<br />\n尤其係屎忽,腳同背<br />\n但睇落係毫無痕跡既<br />\n即係無紅無一舊舊咩都無<br />\n得個痕字<br />\n<br />\n有冇解教方法"},{"pid":"4fdaecbf1ec62231e2946bcf2a7196d2fe406f5a","tid":172190,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"我通常係唔流一排汗就會咁 我解讀係係時候要做下運動流汗"},{"pid":"69a62c9386e439a22b473a9d291a5cf7c06a08ac","tid":172190,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"頭最痕"},{"pid":"103087445e6dbe57a9d824aaef506bb2b6a8858c","tid":172190,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:22:20.000Z","msg":"腳會勁痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb5156a88f34c7713856e09d5bd5864d1dc883f","tid":172190,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e133c0945494c85ab62818dcff0a236049ff87cf","tid":172190,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"個頭痕到比蟻咬一樣"},{"pid":"411913d036daf0e97202f951ff1abc14a40e2f01","tid":172190,"uid":79421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一熱就會拿住拿住咁痕 背脊同頭最嚴重"},{"pid":"538c0b5fba26391d13b9ba7bec90c80f8601aea0","tid":172190,"uid":27143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:29:36.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"febf2eae3f802cb96433e6336d47b4839f3319fa","tid":172190,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2