kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概一年前開始係咁 以前無事 <br />\n一開始係每日某個時候對腳掌就會痕到仆街 r都無用 一r就出紅點 唔r佢都有紅點但無咁明顯<br />\n而家一出汗，熱，焗 食辣野 就成身痕 搞到而家跑步都好辛苦 好痕<br />\n一般發作5-15mins就退<br />\n大家每次發作時間幾耐？係咪無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce88badfa0a59f22af0c6b3bd9279309d990361","tid":172190,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩屌我以為無人明白我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 皮膚因為遺傳問題極乾燥</blockquote><br />\n但咁多年黎我已經發展到可以冥想散熱 (我估有d似西藏高僧冥想整乾濕床單) 利申 無吹水"},{"pid":"483390878b984a82626e1e136ff267d257e5d514","tid":172190,"uid":90641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概一年前開始係咁 以前無事 <br />\n一開始係每日某個時候對腳掌就會痕到仆街 r都無用 一r就出紅點 唔r佢都有紅點但無咁明顯<br />\n而家一出汗，熱，焗 食辣野 就成身痕 搞到而家跑步都好辛苦 好痕<br />\n一般發作5-15mins就退<br />\n大家每次發作時間幾耐？係咪無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰種痕唔係皮膚乾燥嗰種 係啲皮膚下面發出黎 如果同我差唔多既人應該明我講咩"},{"pid":"961cded7da0fd0ec78b21994a6f2b8c702dbcaca","tid":172190,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"個背一熱就痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125d96bfe0e69b17